summary: Adds a Witch Doctor to the Warrens, with a new weapon and armor set.
descriptionHtml:
Description
=======-----=======
The Witch Doctor, a feared Forsworn alchemist so powerful that he chooses to live where he pleases. He decided to live in the Warrens, where many Forsworn live in Markarth. He has specially made weapons and armor, such as a boomstick (lol), a powerfully poisoned staff, and amazing armor to fit the theme. If you want to get that armor, you\'ll get a fight first.

     Change Log
=======-----=======
Version 1.0: 
-Initial release.
